<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Only 4 pets can attack any given mob at the same time.  Having 6 magicians would rock, but you'd still want an enchanter to keep the mana flowing, so make a 7 person group.  Have 5 in the group to start with.  Give #6 an invite, but have him not accept yet.  Have #6 give #7 an invite, but have #7 not accept yet.  Now have #6 accept invite, then #7 accept 6's invite.  <p>

#7 will not show up in group status window, nor will he recieve group chat.  He will share exp.  #7 will show himself & #6 as being in a group.  #7 can send group chat to everybody, just can't receive any.  Known bug since Beta.  No ETA on fix.<p>

Either way, if you're fighting single mobs it's a waste to have more than 4 pet classes.</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
